spec_data.Description:
The Release Notes provide high-level coverage of the improvements
and additions that have been implemented in Red Hat Enterprise
Linux 7.0. For detailed documentation on all changes to Red
Hat Enterprise Linux for the 7.0 release, refer to the
Technical Notes.
